parametersMap.apmTraceExplorerQuery: show traces max(username) as Username,max(traceduration) as MaxTraceDuration,sum(PageResponseTime) as TotalResponseTime,sum(PageViews) as PageViews,sum(ErrorCount) as ErrorCount,count(*) as Traces,avg(ConnectTime) as ConnectTime,max(TraceLatestSpanEndTime) - min(TraceFirstSpanStartTime) as SessionDuration,min(TraceFirstSpanStartTime) as StartTime,max(TraceLatestSpanEndTime) as EndTime where sessionid in (show traces sessionid where (Component in ('BROWSER', 'RUEI') and TraceRootSpanDuration > 1000) first 100000 rows) group by sessionid
show spans username,component,error, traceid,DbOracleSqlId,SpanDuration,StartTime where (component in ('RUEI','JDBC') and spanduration > 1000)  order by StartTime desc
show traces username, sessionid, * where traceid in (show spans traceid where ThreadName like '[STUCK] %)''' first 1000 rows)

dashboards.description: This dashboard is used to import the set of custom trace widgets. It can be deleted after the import is complete.

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'EBS Concurrent Request Logs' and Label != 'Request Resubmitted' | stats unique(Program) as Program, unique(Status) as Status, unique(Label) as Label, min('Event Start Time') as StartTime, max('Event End Time') as EndTime, unique('Error IDs') as Error by 'Request ID' | eval RequestTimeMins = if(EndTime != null, (EndTime - StartTime) / 60000, (now() - StartTime) / 60000) | sort -StartTime | fields -EndTime | where StartTime != null

savedSearches.description: Problem labels identified in Concurrent Request Logs, Transaction Logs, Processing Logs

uiConfig.queryString: 'Problem Priority' != null and 'Log Source' in ('EBS Concurrent Request Logs', 'EBS Concurrent Manager Logs', 'EBS Internal Concurrent Manager Logs', 'EBS Transaction Manager Logs') | eval pos = indexOf(Entity, '/') | eval entity = if(pos != -1, substr(Entity, 0, pos), Entity) | stats count by Label, entity
'Log Source' = 'FMW WLS Server Logs' and Label != null | stats count as logrecords by Label | sort -logrecords

'Entity Type' in ('WebLogic Server', 'Oracle Internet Directory', 'Oracle HTTP Server', 'Oracle Access Management Server', 'WebLogic Domain', OC4J) and 'Error ID' != 'bea-000000' and 'Error ID' != null | stats count as errors, trend by 'Error ID' | top limit = 10 errors
